## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="ef2a1-198">下列主控台應用程式擷取所有可見的 OLE DB 提供者的相關資訊，並顯示在主控台視窗中的資訊。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="ef2a1-198">The following console application retrieves information about all the visible OLE DB providers and displays the information in the console window.</span></span>  
  
